provisions.content:
_In this Act, unless there is anything repugnant in the subject or context,___
“enrolled” means enrolled or re-enrolled in the Pakistan Territorial Force under this Act;
“non-commissioned officer” means a person holding non-commissioned rank in the Pakistan
Territorial Force, and includes an acting non-commissioned officer;
“officer” means a commissioned officer or a junior commissioned officer;
“prescribed” means prescribed by rules made under this Act.
